<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Connect | Deangarden</title>

<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box}

body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Inter,sans-serif;
  background:#f6f4ec;
  color:#142416;
}

.page{
  max-width:880px;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:34px 20px 48px;
}

.brand{
  text-align:center;
  margin-bottom:34px;
}

.brand h1{
  font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
  font-size:clamp(2rem,8vw,3.6rem);
  letter-spacing:.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-weight:400;
  margin:0;
}

.brand p{
  margin-top:12px;
  color:#557055;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  letter-spacing:.22em;
  font-size:.78rem;
}

.card{
  background:white;
  border-radius:30px;
  padding:30px 24px;
  box-shadow:0 20px 70px rgba(20,35,22,.13);
}

.profile{
  text-align:center;
}

.portrait{
  width:132px;
  height:132px;
  object-fit:cover;
  border-radius:50%;
  margin:0 auto 22px;
  display:block;
  border:1px solid rgba(20,35,22,.12);
}

h2{
  font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",serif;
  font-size:2.1rem;
  font-weight:400;
  margin:0;
}

.role{
  margin-top:8px;
  color:#456847;
  font-size:1.05rem;
}

.intro{
  margin:28px auto 30px;
  max-width:620px;
  font-size:1.05rem;
  line-height:1.7;
  color:#263b29;
}

.links{
  display:grid;
  gap:14px;
  margin:26px 0 34px;
}

.link{
  display:block;
  padding:18px 20px;
  border-radius:18px;
  text-align:center;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:650;
  background:#17351d;
  color:white;
}

.link.secondary{
  background:#eef2e8;
  color:#142416;
  border:1px solid rgba(20,35,22,.12);
}

.grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:28px;
  border-top:1px solid #e3e7dc;
  padding-top:28px;
}

.section h3{
  font-size:.78rem;
  letter-spacing:.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:#557055;
  margin:0 0 14px;
}

.tags{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap:10px;
}

.tag{
  background:#eef2e8;
  border-radius:999px;
  padding:10px 14px;
  font-size:.9rem;
}

.footer{
  text-align:center;
  margin-top:34px;
  font-size:.9rem;
  color:#60705f;
}

.footer a{
  color:#17351d;
  text-decoration:none;
}

@media(max-width:680px){
  .page{padding:26px 16px 40px}
  .card{padding:28px 20px;border-radius:26px}
  .portrait{width:118px;height:118px}
  h2{font-size:1.9rem}
  .intro{text-align:left;font-size:1rem}
  .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:26px}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<main class="page">

  <section class="brand">
    <h1>Deangarden</h1>
    <p>Landscape Intelligence</p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">

    <div class="profile">
      <img class="portrait" src="images/portrait.png" alt="Ikaraam Ullah portrait">

      <h2>Connect with Deangarden</h2>

      <div class="role">
        Ikaraam Ullah<br>
        Solutions Architect
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="intro">
      Deangarden brings together robotics, remote sensing and digital twins
      to build persistent landscape intelligence that helps observe,
      understand and steward natural environments.
      <br><br>
      I welcome conversations with people and organisations working across
      environmental technology, autonomous systems, sensing, conservation
      and resilient landscape management.
    </p>

    <div class="links">
      <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ikaraam/">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      <a class="link secondary" href="mailto:contact@deangarden.org">contact@deangarden.org</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>Current Focus</h3>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Landscape Intelligence</span>
          <span class="tag">Robotics</span>
          <span class="tag">Remote Sensing</span>
          <span class="tag">Digital Twins</span>
          <span class="tag">Biodiversity</span>
          <span class="tag">Environmental Monitoring</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Open to Conversations With</h3>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Universities</span>
          <span class="tag">Environmental organisations</span>
          <span class="tag">Technology partners</span>
          <span class="tag">Conservation practitioners</span>
          <span class="tag">Landowners</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <div class="footer">
    Building landscape intelligence for natural environments.<br><br>
    <a href="/">← Back to Deangarden</a>
  </div>

</main>
</body>
</html>